            "id": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/22/systemctl%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEaria2%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8/",
            "url": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/22/systemctl%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEaria2%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8/",
            "title": "systemctl管理方式下设置aria2开机启动",
            "date_published": "2021-06-22T02:05:32.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"1、aria2开机启动文件配置—aria2-service\"><a href=\"#1、aria2开机启动文件配置—aria2-service\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、aria2开机启动文件配置—aria2.service\"></a>1、aria2开机启动文件配置—<code>aria2.service</code></h1><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">k@yk-pc:~$ sudo nano /usr/lib/systemd/system/aria2.service<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>输入以下内容：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">[Unit]<br>Description=Aria2 Service<br>After=network.target<br><br>[Service]<br>ExecStart=/usr/bin/aria2c --conf-path=/etc/aria2/aria2.conf<br><br>[Install]<br>WantedBy=default.target<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>写入<code>ctrl+o</code>，保存 <code>Enter</code>，退出<code>ctrl+x</code><br>拷贝到<code>/etc/systemd/user</code> 目录下<br>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">k@yk-pc:~$ sudo cp /usr/lib/systemd/system/aria2.service /etc/systemd/system<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"2-设置开机启动\"><a href=\"#2-设置开机启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.设置开机启动\"></a>2.设置开机启动</h1><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">yk@yk-pc:/usr/lib/systemd/system$ systemctl <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">enable</span> aria2.service<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>提示<code>Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/default.target.wants/aria2.service → /etc/systemd/system/aria2.service.</code>设置成功</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/P3TERX/aria2.conf\">一键安装及配置开源项目：</a></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "systemctl",
                "启动服务",
                "aria2"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/20/Debian10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fsystemctl%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8BNginx%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8/",
            "url": "https://owenyk.github.io/2021/06/20/Debian10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fsystemctl%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8BNginx%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8/",
            "title": "Debian10系统systemctl服务管理方式下Nginx设置开机启动",
            "date_published": "2021-06-20T12:05:32.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>linux服务目前主要有service和systemctl两种管理方式，systemd是Linux系统最新的初始化系统(init),作用是提高系统的启动速度，尽可能启动较少的进程，尽可能更多进程并发启动，对应的进程管理命令是systemctl。  </p>\n<h1 id=\"1-建立服务文件\"><a href=\"#1-建立服务文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 建立服务文件\"></a>1. 建立服务文件</h1><p>命令 <code>vim /usr/lib/systemd/system/nginx.service</code>，进入文件，将以下代码复制进去保存即可<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">[Unit]<br>Description=nginx  <br>After=network.target  <br><br>[Service]<br>Type=forking<br>ExecStart=/usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/nginx/sbin/nginx<br>ExecReload=/bin/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -s reload<br>ExecStop=/bin/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -s stop<br>PrivateTmp=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span><br><br>[Install]<br>WantedBy=multi-user.target<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>参数说明：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">[Unit]:服务的说明<br>Description=:描述服务<br>After=:描述服务类别<br><br>[Service]服务运行参数的设置<br>Type=forking是后台运行的形式<br>ExecStart=为服务的具体运行命令<br>ExecReload=为重启命令<br>ExecStop=为停止命令<br>PrivateTmp=True表示给服务分配独立的临时空间<br>注意：启动、重启、停止命令全部要求使用绝对路径<br><br>[Install]服务安装的相关设置，可设置为多用户<br>WantedBy=multi-user.target<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"2-设置文件权限并使文件生效\"><a href=\"#2-设置文件权限并使文件生效\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 设置文件权限并使文件生效\"></a>2. 设置文件权限并使文件生效</h1><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo chmod 755 /usr/lib/systemd/system/nginx.service<br>systemctl daemon-reload<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"3-设置开机启动\"><a href=\"#3-设置开机启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.设置开机启动\"></a>3.设置开机启动</h1><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">systemctl <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">enable</span> nginx.service<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><br>只有返回类似 <code>Created symlink from /etc/systemd/system/multi-user.target.wants/nginx.service → /etc/systemd/system/nginx.service</code>提示才能够确定设置成功。如果不是请检查上面的文件.  </p>\n<h1 id=\"4-其他命令\"><a href=\"#4-其他命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 其他命令\"></a>4. 其他命令</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter hljs\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"hljs code-wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">systemctl is-enabled servicename.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#查询服务是否开机启动</span><br>systemctl <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">enable</span> *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#开机运行服务</span><br>systemctl <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">disable</span> *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#取消开机运行</span><br>systemctl start *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#启动服务</span><br>systemctl stop *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#停止服务</span><br>systemctl restart *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#重启服务</span><br>systemctl reload *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#重新加载服务配置文件</span><br>systemctl status *.service <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#查询服务运行状态</span><br>systemctl --failed <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#显示启动失败的服务</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>转载于<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ren365880/article/details/103597006\">nginx在systemctl方式开机自启动</a><br>参考资料：  </p>\n<p>1.<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/seasen/p/12603017.html\">nginx添加service以及随开机启动:</a>  </p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Debian",
                "Nginx",
                "systemctl",
                "启动服务"
            ]
